            "content": "# Commands\n\nActive contributors: Arman Bolat, Luke Alvoeiro, shashank-factory, theo, Leo Tchourakov\n\nThe CLI registers 50+ slash commands via a central registry in `src/commands/index.ts`. Users invoke these with `/command` during an interactive session, or some are available as top-level CLI arguments.\n\n## Command registration\n\nCommands are defined as objects with metadata (name, description, aliases) and an execute function. They're registered via `commandRegistry.register()` in `src/commands/index.ts`. Custom commands can be loaded dynamically via `CustomCommandsLoader` and `SkillCommandsLoader`.\n\n## Command categories\n\n### Session management\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `/new` | `new.ts` | Start a new session |\n| `/sessions` | `sessions.ts` | List recent sessions |\n| `/fork` | `fork.ts` | Fork the current session |\n| `/rename` | `rename.ts` | Rename the current session |\n| `/share` | `share.ts` | Share a session link |\n| `/copy` | `copy.ts` | Copy session content to clipboard |\n| `/rewind` | `rewind.ts` | Rewind to a previous message |\n| `/compact` | `compact.ts` | Compact conversation history |\n| `/clear` | `clear.ts` | Clear the screen |\n| `/favorite` | `favorite.ts` | Mark session as favorite |\n\n### AI agent\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `/model` | `model.ts` | Switch LLM model |\n| `/fast` | `fast.ts` | Toggle fast mode (cheaper model) |\n| `/language` | `language.ts` | Set response language |\n| `/cost` | `cost.ts` | Show token usage and cost |\n| `/stats` | `stats/` | Session and usage statistics |\n\n### Missions and skills\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `/mission` | `mission.ts` | Start a mission |\n| `/missions` | `missions.ts` | List missions |\n| `/enter-mission` | `enter-mission.ts` | Enter an existing mission |\n| `/exit-mission` | `exit-mission.ts` | Exit current mission |\n| `/skills` | `skills.ts` | List available skills |\n| `/create-