            "content": "# Packages\n\nThe monorepo has 20 packages under `packages/`, organized as npm workspaces. These provide shared libraries consumed by the applications.\n\n## Core packages\n\n| Package | npm name | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| [common](./common/index.md) | `@factory/common` | Shared types, enums, API contracts, protocol schemas |\n| [droid-core](./droid-core/index.md) | `@factory/droid-core` | AI agent core: LLM integrations, tools, prompts, streaming |\n| [daemon-core](./daemon-core.md) | `@factory/daemon-core` | Daemon server logic, relay integration, terminal management |\n\n## UI packages\n\n| Package | npm name | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| [core-ui](./core-ui.md) | `@factory/core-ui` | Design system primitives (Box, Button, Input, etc.) |\n| [component-library](./component-library.md) | `@factory/component-library` | Feature-level UI components (chat, settings, billing) |\n| [frontend](./frontend/index.md) | `@factory/frontend` | Shared React features, hooks, and services for web/desktop |\n\n## Infrastructure packages\n\n| Package | npm name | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| [logging](./other.md) | `@factory/logging` | Structured logging, Sentry integration, MetaError classes |\n| [models](./other.md) | `@factory/models` | Firestore data models and type definitions |\n| [services](./other.md) | `@factory/services` | Shared service layer (settings, plugins, session search) |\n| [environment](./other.md) | `@factory/environment` | Typed environment variable access |\n| [runtime](./other.md) | `@factory/runtime` | Runtime utilities and auth helpers |\n| [utils](./other.md) | `@factory/utils` | Common utility functions |\n\n## Development packages\n\n| Package | npm name | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| [eslint-config](./other.md) | `@factory/eslint-config` | Custom ESLint rules and shared configs |\n| [test-utils](./other.md) | `@factory/test-utils` | Test utilities and helpers |\n| [updater](./other.md) | `@factory/updater` | CLI/daemon auto-update mechanism |\n\n## Protocol packages\n\n| Package | npm name | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| [daemon-client](./other.md) | `@factory/daemon-client` | Client library for daemon communication |\n| [droid-sdk](./other.md) | `@factory/droid-sdk` | SDK for building droid integrations |\n| [mcp](./other.md) | `@factory/mcp` | Model Context Protocol integration |\n| [signal-core](./other.md) | `@factory/signal-core` | Signal server core library |\n\n## Dependency flow\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    Apps[Apps] --> Frontend[frontend]\n    Apps --> DroidCore[droid-core]\n    Apps --> DaemonCore[daemon-core]\n    Frontend --> CoreUI[core-ui]\n    Frontend --> ComponentLib[component-library]\n    Frontend --> Common[common]\n    DroidCore --> Common\n    DaemonCore --> Common\n    ComponentLib --> CoreUI\n    All[All packages] --> Logging[logging]\n    All --> Utils[utils]\n```\n\n`@factory/common` is the most imported package -- it defines the type contracts that all other packages depend on.\n",
