            "content": "# LLM integration\n\nActive contributors: Luke Alvoeiro, l30t, Alvin Sng, factory-sherry\n\nThe LLM integration layer in `packages/droid-core/src/llms/` provides a unified interface for multiple AI model providers. It abstracts away provider-specific API differences so the rest of the codebase works with a single message and response format.\n\n## Supported providers\n\n| Provider | Models | API style |\n|---|---|---|\n| Anthropic | Claude 3.5, Claude 4 (Opus, Sonnet) | Messages API with streaming |\n| OpenAI | GPT-4o, o1, o3 | Chat completions with streaming |\n| Google | Gemini 2.0, 2.5 | Generative AI API with streaming |\n\nModel definitions and capabilities are tracked in `packages/common/src/llm/`. Each model entry specifies context window size, supported features (vision, tool use, thinking), and pricing.\n\n## Streaming architecture\n\n```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    Request[Completion request] --> Provider[Provider adapter]\n    Provider --> Stream[SSE/streaming response]\n    Stream --> Parser[Stream parser]\n    Parser --> Tokens[Text tokens]\n    Parser --> ToolCalls[Tool call chunks]\n    Tokens --> Assembler[Response assembler]\n    ToolCalls --> Assembler\n    Assembler --> Complete[Complete response]\n```\n\nThe streaming layer in `src/streaming/` processes responses incrementally:\n1. Provider adapter sends the request in provider-specific format\n2. Stream parser handles SSE events from the provider API\n3. Tokens and tool call chunks are extracted as they arrive\n4. Response assembler builds the complete message for the conversation\n\n## BYOK support\n\nUsers can provide their own API keys (Bring Your Own Key) instead of using Factory's proxied access. BYOK configuration is stored in the user's local settings and routed through the CLI's `src/llm-proxy/` layer.\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `src/llms/` | Provider-specific adapters |\n| `src/streaming/` | Streaming response processing |\n| `packages/common/src/llm/` | Model definitions and capabilities |\n| `apps/cli/src/llm-proxy/` | Local LLM proxy for BYOK |\n| `apps/cli/src/hooks/useLLMStreaming.ts` | CLI-side streaming hook |\n",
