            "content": "# Daemon core\n\nActive contributors: factory-jerry, factory-sherry, shashank-factory, Luke Alvoeiro, factory-octavian\n\n`@factory/daemon-core` provides the server logic for the Droid daemon -- the background process that manages sessions, relays messages, and bridges clients to the backend.\n\n## Architecture\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    CLI[CLI Process] -->|stdin/stdout| DaemonCore\n    WebApp[Web/Desktop] -->|WebSocket| Server[HTTP/WS Server]\n    Server --> DaemonCore\n    DaemonCore --> Relay[Relay Connection]\n    DaemonCore --> Terminal[Terminal Manager]\n    DaemonCore --> Automations[Automations Engine]\n    DaemonCore --> Services[Service Layer]\n```\n\n## Directory layout\n\n```\npackages/daemon-core/src/\n  DaemonCore.ts         # Main daemon class\n  index.ts              # Package exports\n  constants.ts          # Configuration constants\n  types.ts              # Type definitions\n  automations/          # Automated workflow execution\n  code-server/          # Code server integration\n  droid/                # Droid process spawning and management\n  relay/                # Relay WebSocket connection\n  server/               # HTTP and WebSocket server\n    handlers/           # Request handlers (droid-request-handler.ts is 5095 lines)\n  services/             # Internal services\n  terminal/             # Terminal session management\n  utils/                # Utility functions\n```\n\n## DaemonCore class\n\n`DaemonCore.ts` is the central orchestrator. It:\n- Starts the HTTP/WebSocket server for client connections\n- Manages the relay connection for cross-machine access\n- Spawns and monitors droid CLI processes for each session\n- Routes JSON-RPC messages between clients and droid processes\n- Manages terminal sessions for web-based terminal access\n\n## Request handling\n\n`server/handlers/droid-request-handler.ts` is the largest file in the package at 5095 lines. It handles all JSON-RPC requests from clients, dispatching them to the appropriate droid process or internal service.\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `src/DaemonCore.ts` | Main daemon orchestrator |\n| `src/server/` | HTTP/WebSocket server |\n| `src/server/handlers/droid-request-handler.ts` | JSON-RPC request routing |\n| `src/relay/` | Relay WebSocket connection |\n| `src/terminal/` | Terminal session management |\n| `src/droid/` | Droid process lifecycle |\n| `src/automations/` | Automated workflow execution |\n",
