            "content": "# LLM streaming\n\nDroid supports multiple LLM providers through a unified streaming interface. Messages are sent to the provider's API and responses arrive as a stream of tokens and tool call chunks.\n\n## Provider support\n\n| Provider | Package | Models |\n|---|---|---|\n| Anthropic | `@anthropic-ai/sdk` | Claude 3.5, Claude 4 Opus/Sonnet |\n| OpenAI | `openai` | GPT-4o, o1, o3 |\n| Google | `@google/genai` | Gemini 2.0, 2.5 |\n\nModel definitions live in `packages/common/src/llm/`. The CLI's `/model` command lets users switch models mid-session.\n\n## Streaming flow\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant CLI as useLLMStreaming\n    participant Core as droid-core streaming\n    participant Provider as LLM Provider API\n\n    CLI->>Core: Send message array\n    Core->>Provider: POST /messages (streaming)\n    Provider-->>Core: SSE: text delta\n    Core-->>CLI: Token callback\n    Provider-->>Core: SSE: tool_use start\n    Core-->>CLI: Tool call callback\n    Provider-->>Core: SSE: message_stop\n    Core-->>CLI: Completion callback\n```\n\n## Implementation layers\n\n1. **`packages/droid-core/src/llms/`** -- provider-specific adapters that translate between the internal message format and each provider's API\n2. **`packages/droid-core/src/streaming/`** -- streaming response parser that extracts tokens and tool calls from SSE events\n3. **`apps/cli/src/hooks/useLLMStreaming.ts`** -- React hook that connects the streaming layer to the TUI, handling state updates and rendering\n4. **`apps/cli/src/hooks/createLLMStreamingCore.ts`** -- core streaming logic shared between TUI and exec modes\n\n## BYOK\n\nUsers can provide their own API keys via `/settings` or the `--byok` flag. When BYOK is active, requests go directly to the provider instead of through Factory's backend proxy. The routing logic lives in `apps/cli/src/llm-proxy/`.\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `packages/droid-core/src/llms/` | Provider adapters |\n| `packages/droid-core/src/streaming/` | Stream parser |\n| `apps/cli/src/hooks/useLLMStreaming.ts` | TUI streaming hook |\n| `apps/cli/src/hooks/createLLMStreamingCore.ts` | Core streaming logic |\n| `apps/cli/src/llm-proxy/` | BYOK proxy routing |\n| `packages/common/src/llm/` | Model definitions |\n",
