            "content": "# Tooling\n\n## Build system\n\n**Turborepo** orchestrates builds across the monorepo. It handles task dependencies between workspaces, caching, and parallel execution. Configuration is in `turbo.json`.\n\n**npm workspaces** manage package dependencies. Workspace definitions are in the root `package.json` under `workspaces`.\n\n## Linting and formatting\n\n| Tool | Purpose | Command |\n|---|---|---|\n| ESLint | Code linting | `npm run lint` or `npm run fix` |\n| Prettier | Code formatting | Integrated into `npm run fix` |\n| Stylelint | CSS linting | `npm run stylelint` |\n| Knip | Unused export detection | `npm run knip` |\n\n`npm run fix` is preferred over `npm run lint` -- it auto-fixes what it can.\n\n## Custom ESLint rules\n\n`@factory/eslint-config` in `packages/eslint-config/` contains 57 custom rules under `rules/`. Key rules:\n- `factory/enum-file-organization` -- enums must be in `enums.ts`\n- `factory/types-file-organization` -- types must be in `types.ts`\n- `factory/constants-file-organization` -- constants in dedicated files\n- `no-direct-process-env` -- use `@factory/environment` instead of `process.env`\n\nConfigurations: `base.js` (all packages), `frontend.js` (React apps), `backend.js` (Next.js), `factory.js` (Factory-specific rules).\n\n## CI/CD\n\nGitHub Actions workflows in `.github/workflows/` (50+ workflow files):\n- `test.yml`, `test-backend.yml`, `test-cli.yml` -- test suites\n- `typecheck.yml` -- TypeScript checking\n- `eslint.yml`, `format.yml` -- linting and formatting\n- `protocol-manifest.yml` -- protocol compatibility check\n- `deploy-prod.yml`, `deploy-dev-web.yml` -- deployment\n- `cli-release.yml`, `desktop-release.yml` -- binary releases\n- `cli-e2e-tests.yml` -- CLI end-to-end testing\n\n## Key tools\n\n| Tool | Version | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| Node.js | 18.x | Runtime (see `.nvmrc`) |\n| Bun | 1.3.x | CLI/daemon runtime |\n| npm | 11.x | Package manager |\n| Turborepo | 2.6.x | Build orchestrator |\n| Jest | 29.x | Backend/CLI testing |\n| Vitest | -- | Frontend testing |\n| Playwright | -- | E2E testing |\n| Husky | -- | Git hooks |\n",
