            "content": "# Security\n\n## Authentication\n\nAll API access requires a WorkOS session token. The backend validates tokens on every request via middleware in `apps/backend/src/middleware.ts`. See [Authentication](./features/authentication.md).\n\n## Secret management\n\n- Environment variables are managed via `@factory/environment` (typed access, no raw `process.env`)\n- The `@factory/logging` package automatically scrubs secrets from log output before sending to Sentry\n- CLI credentials are stored with restricted file permissions. `apps/cli/src/utils/filePermissions.ts` ensures secure permissions on startup.\n\n## Input validation\n\nAPI routes validate request payloads. The error handling system uses typed error classes (`ResponseError400BadRequest`, etc.) to ensure consistent error responses.\n\n## Trust boundaries\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    User[User Device] -->|Authenticated| Daemon\n    Daemon -->|Token-based| Backend\n    Backend -->|OAuth| Integrations[Third-party services]\n    Backend -->|API Key| LLMProviders[LLM Providers]\n    Backend -->|Credentials| Firestore\n```\n\n- User-to-daemon: local process, trusted\n- Daemon-to-backend: authenticated HTTPS\n- Backend-to-integrations: OAuth tokens per integration\n- Backend-to-LLM: API keys managed server-side (or BYOK)\n\n## Tool execution security\n\nThe CLI's tool execution system includes a risk level assessment:\n- **Low risk**: read-only operations (auto-approved)\n- **Medium risk**: file modifications (may require confirmation)\n- **High risk**: destructive operations, network access (requires explicit approval)\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `apps/backend/src/middleware.ts` | Auth middleware |\n| `apps/backend/src/services/workos/` | Token validation |\n| `apps/cli/src/utils/filePermissions.ts` | Secure file permissions |\n| `packages/logging/` | Secret scrubbing |\n| `packages/environment/` | Typed env var access |\n| `packages/common/src/security/` | Security types |\n",
            "file_path": "/Users/jonathanlucuix-andre/Documents/test-repos/factory-mono/droid-wiki/security.md"
