            "content": "# How to monitor\n\nFactory uses multiple observability systems to track application health, errors, and performance.\n\n| System | Purpose | Integration point |\n|---|---|---|\n| [Sentry](./logging.md) | Error tracking and alerting | `@factory/logging`, `@sentry/node`, `@sentry/nextjs` |\n| [Axiom](./logging.md) | Log aggregation and querying | CLI and backend log shipping |\n| [Datadog](./metrics.md) | Metrics, dashboards, CI visibility | Backend and infrastructure metrics |\n| Segment | Analytics events | `apps/backend/src/services/segment/` |\n\nSee [Logging](./logging.md) and [Metrics](./metrics.md) for details.\n",
